<h2>Hi there.</h2>
<p class='first'><strong>Picalag</strong> is an intelligent unified calendar for Manchester. It was developed on top of Calagator as a MSc project. It is designed to learn your interests and help you to find relevant events to attend for a day of a night out.</p>

<h4>Get Started</h4>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dEpyQVFFSHFvYXhaa2ZENnZqTy0xVGc6MQ" target="_blank">Complete the initial form for the evaluation here</a></li>
  <li>Register and/or log in</li>
  <li>Find your favorite venues and mark them by clicking "add to my favorites" link on the right panel</li>
  <li>Start browsing events that interest you</li>
  <li>You will find our recommendations in "My Picalag"</li>
  <li>To see what's on your favorite venues and get suggestions about venues go to "favorite venues" section</li>
  <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dDctSl9lYmZrQ0d5aTFJaExoMEhXQ3c6MQ" target="_blank">Please do not forget to complete the short form after each browsing session to give your feedbacks here</a></li>
</ul>

<h4>Subscribe To</h4>
<ul>
  <li><%= link_to "iCalendar feed", url_for(:controller => "events", :action => "index", :protocol => "webcal", :only_path => false)+".ics" %></li>
  <li><%= link_to "Atom feed", events_url(:format => "atom") %></li>
</ul>
